cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.GR, cs.CL. 

The paper deals with the task of interactive annotation of segmentation datasets using deep learning techniques. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses the use of Reinforcement Learning, which falls under the category of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper proposes a new CNN encoder architecture and uses a Graph Neural Network, which are both topics related to cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also discusses the use of interactive annotation, which falls under the category of cs.GR (Graphics). Finally, the paper discusses the use of natural language processing techniques to improve the annotation process, which falls under the category of cs.CL (Computation and Language).
